dc_title_s: Geologic atlas of Pine County, Minnesota, C-13, Part A, Plate 6, Sinkhole distribution, Depth to Bedrock, and Bedrock Topography
dc_description_s: Map showing the thickness (depth to bedrock) of unconsolidated sediments (Quaternary glacial and stream materials) over the bedrock surface and elevation of the bedrock surface (bedrock topography), scale 1:200,000; map showing locations of sinkholes and sinkhole cross sections, scale 1:100,000, Pine County.
